{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b2fb16c876","title":"札记和片断 - 化学","origin":"","is_range_date":true,"dates":[{"id":"31d7e2c388","index":0,"year":1873,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"a26638f49c","index":1,"year":1883,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"b2fb16c876"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","name":"自然辩证法（人民出版社1971年版）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"恩格斯，人民出版社1971年版","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives4/main/0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"a80dd40419","name":"恩格斯"}]},"publication_details":{"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a85d9ecf94","type":"paragraph","text":"[化学了","index":0,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"30791cb575","type":"paragraph","text":"光*","index":1,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"27d6ac3b45","type":"paragraph","text":"常","index":2,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"09e4625938","type":"paragraph","text":"关于实在的化学上一致的物质的观念——不管它多么古老一—是和直到拉瓦锡时还广泛流传的幼稚见解完全一致的，这种幼稚见解认为：两个物体的化学亲和力，是基于它们每个都含有一个共同的第三物体（柯普《发展》第105页）246","index":3,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"02e500ffc8","type":"paragraph","text":"常","index":4,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"3ae78e6c17","type":"paragraph","text":"站","index":5,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"903f43de2a","type":"paragraph","text":"茶","index":6,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"ecce60c2cd","type":"paragraph","text":"旧有的、方便的、适合于过去流行的实践的方法，怎样移到其他领域中并且在那里变成障碍：在化学中，有化合物成分的百分率计算法，它是掩盖化合物的定比和倍比定律的最好不过的方法，它也确实相当长时期地拖盖了这个定律","index":7,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"bc5fd9b34f","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":8,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"09b06cf522","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":9,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"8066a65c1d","type":"paragraph","text":"米","index":10,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"e004dde317","type":"paragraph","text":"化学中的新时代是随着原子论开始的（所以，近代化学之交不是拉瓦锡，而是道尔顿），相应地，物理学中的新时代是随着分子论开始的（是从运动形式互相转化的发现开始的，这在形式上虽然不同，但在本质上不过是这一过程的另一个方面）。新的原子论和所有已往的原子论的区别，在于它不主张（搬开才不说）物质只是非连续的，而主张各个不同阶段的各个非连续的部分（以太原子、化学原子、物体、天体）是各种不同的关节点，这些关节点决定一般物质的各种不同的质的存在形式—直到失重和排岸的形式。","index":11,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"1bf1771034","type":"paragraph","text":"兴站","index":12,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"935e548a53","type":"paragraph","text":"米量到质的转化：最简单的例子是氧和臭氧，在这里2:3引起了二者甚至在气味方面的一些完全相异的属性。化学也只用分子中原子数目的不同去说明其他的同素异性体","index":13,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"5b017e6489","type":"paragraph","text":"米","index":14,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"84f3408bfe","type":"paragraph","text":"基","index":15,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"5e20f1760d","type":"paragraph","text":"开","index":16,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"},{"id":"c153423a2e","type":"paragraph","text":"名称的意义。在有机化学中，一个物体的意义以及它的名称，不再仅仅由它的构成来决定，而更多地是由它在它所隶属的系列中的位置来决定。因此，如果我们发现了某个物体属于某个这样的系列，那末它的旧名称就变成了理解的障碍，而必须代之以表明这个系列的名称（烧烧等等）。","index":17,"publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876"}],"page":{"id":"a29ecfdfbd","publicationId":"0bbdba91-48e9-4148-9ec2-38bf6792cca7","articleId":"b2fb16c876","start":275,"end":276}}}},"__N_SSG":true}